Okta provides enterprise companies identity management and security for the cloud. As organizations adopt cloud services such as Salesforce.com, Google Apps, NetSuite, Workday, etc., mission critical data is shifting from locked-down environments behind the firewall to dispersed sites across the web. Okta provides IT the tools to manage and secure their cloud applications as if they were on premise, including, single sign-on, automated user management, multi-factor authentication and reporting/auditing.
